== Zvimwe Zviumbwa ==

Gokomakonya (Diagonal) - iri izwi rinoreva mutsetse inobva pagonya uchipfuura nepagoko kuenda pane rimwe gonya rakatarisana nerekutanga. Uyu mutsetse unobatanidza goko (centre) negonya mbiri. Goko regonyazhinji rinenge riri nhambwe yakaenzana kubva pagonya dzose dzegonyazhinji.

Zhumwi (Prism) - chiumbwa chine ''nzenda'' nhatu (3-dimensional) chinotaridzika kunge chiumbwa chine nzenda mbiri chakatatamurwa zvichitevedza kunoenda mutwi unobva pahwaro. (Appears like a 2-dimensional shape that has been translated along a line perpendicular to the base, so that all parallel cross-sections have the same shape) 

Mucheko (Cross-section) - iri shoko rinoreva uso hunoonekwa kana zhumwi rachekwa zvakati sambamba nehwaro hwezhumwi. 

Gonyaina sambamba (Parallelogram) - ichi chiumbwa chine mativi mana - mativi maviri akati sambamba anenge akaenzana - uye gonya mbiri dzinobatanidzwa negokomagonya dzinenge dzakaenzana.

Charaka (Cone) - iri izwi rinoreva chiumbwa chine uso huviri, humwe huri hwaro hwedenderedzwa hwakati sandarara hwepiri huri uso hunopfirira hwaro kusvika ''pachisuvi (apex)''. Nguva zhinji chisuvi chinenge chakaita mutwi negoko redenderedzwa riri pauso hunova hwaro. Shoko reShona iri rinotodzana necharaka chinowanikwa paduwo rinoteyeswa hove rine kuumbwa kwe ''cone'' - hove inopinda nekwakapamhama, yave mukati charaka chakamanika zvokuti hove itadze kubuda.

Dumba (Pyramid)- iri shoko rinotoredzera kubva pachiumbwa chinoonekwa kana tichitema mashanga echigabe nokuamisa kuita matumba. Tiri muchidzidzo Kupimanzimbo kune marudzi ematumba anodanwa zvakasiyana zvichienderana nechiumbwa chiri pahwaro hwedumba racho. Sokuti kune ''dumba regonyanhanhatu'' (hexagonal pyramid)
